---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div class="card">
    <h1>
      What we do
    </h1>
    <p>
      We push human-computer interaction into the future, by focusing on new technologies and developing new methodologies to face the challenges of tomorrow.
    </p>
    <p>
      We’ve worked on using biomarkers as a form of non-verbal user feedback, social robots and AI as a form of administering user studies on a mass scale, and ‘toyification’ as a playful and natural approach to technology user studies
    </p>
    <div class="button-container">
      <a href="/work">
        Read about our work
        <Icon name="arrow-right-bold" class="size-4"/>
      </a>
      <!-- <a href="/">
        Explore our blog
        <Icon name="arrow-right-bold" class="size-4"/>
      </a> -->
    </div>
  </div>

<style>
  .card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: #00000010;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
  }

  .button-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: end;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-self: stretch;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  a {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    background-color: #000;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    color: #FFF;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>